QueryJ
---------------

QueryJ provides a way of ensuring error-free SQL statements,
maintaining SQL simplicity, and allowing statement customization
independent to the developer.
The features include not only SQL handling, but also the generation
of a complete persistence layer from a given deployed relational schema.

The file NEWS summarizes recent changes.

Kawa's copyright is described in the file COPYING.

